{"type": "article", "id": 26917, "title": "苔藓钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-17T06:45:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115753XObgj2ldJwxSkouA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>打算给家里增添一点绿意可以从很多小地方做起，一个以苔藓作钟面的挂钟就是一个不错的选择。设计师 Paul Noktuku 选用挪威的驯鹿苔藓作为材料，大约每 2 千克的生苔藓才能制作一款挂钟，由于经过处理，你也无需为它们浇水。Noktuku 根据颜色还形象地将它们分别命名为夏、秋、冬三款。目前正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mossclock/the-moss-clock\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，夏和秋款的价格为 300 欧元，冬款为 320 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115751XYEyzqAdhRio8Per.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115751EPwoJn0SXDrsHiUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99264706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115752VW3ymsePwQrx4oOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115752xD5Xhl1gs8SOq0Ci.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}